                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol.163va: This is the book of ras Sǝbḥat which he donated to (the church of) St. Michael Nǝhǝb, and his baptismal name is Kidanä Maryam and the names of his children (are) Wäldä Gäbrǝʾel, ʾArʾaya Śǝllase, Wäldä ʾArägäwi, Zä-Mänfäs Qǝddus, Śǝmrätä ʾAb, Säbänä Maryam...</q>
                           A list of the donor´s relatives is given. The note is written in the same hand as that of the main text.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Excerpts from hymns for the Good Friday (?) added in the upper margin: fols. 101v, 102r, 102v, 107v, 108r, 108v, 120v, 121r, 121v, 127v.&#xD;
- Corrections written with blue pen: fol. 51r.&#xD;
- Stamp with the name of the donor (ras Sǝbḥat): fols. 1r, 55r, 95r, 142r, 164r, 174r.</item>
